Test Scenario: User logs into a website
Test case ID:001
steps:
1.Go to website.
2.Enter valid username.
3.Enter valid password.
4.click on login
Expected result: Login successfully and user should enter into dashboard page.
Test Case ID:002
Steps:
1.Go to website.
2.Enter 1234 as username.
3.Enter valid password.
4.Click on login.
Expected result:1.Appropriate error message should be displayed.
2.User should be on same page.
Test case ID:003
steps:
1.Go to website.
2.Enter valid username.
3.Enter invalid password.
4.click on login
Expected result: 1.Appropriate error message of invalid password should be displayed.
2.User should stay on the same page.
Test Case ID:004
Steps:
1.Go to website.
2.Do not enter anything in the username field.
3.Enter valid password.
4.Click on login.
Expected result: 1.Error message "Username should not be empty" should be displayed.
2.User should stay on the same page.
